                "invention-title": [
                    "Energy storage optimal configuration method and system for multi-time scale electric power and electric quantity balance",
                    "面向多时间尺度电力电量平衡的储能优化配置方法及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an energy storage optimization configuration method and system for multi-time scale electric power and electric quantity balance, and the method comprises the steps: obtaining the historical operation data of a system, collecting and sorting the wind power, photovoltaic and load data of the whole year, and obtaining the net load data; performing time decoupling on the net load data by using an STL decomposition method to obtain a trend component, a season component and a residual component of the net load in the whole year; establishing a multi-type energy storage planning model containing hydrogen energy storage and electrochemical energy storage; respectively establishing an energy storage planning constraint model containing various constraints; and solving the multi-type energy storage planning model to obtain an energy storage optimization planning result, wind curtailment and light curtailment conditions in each time period, load shedding conditions in each time period and output conditions of each energy storage. The advantages of hydrogen energy storage and electrochemical energy storage are fully exerted, and long-time energy storage and short-time energy storage are coordinated and matched, so that coupling of different time scales is reduced, and continuous and rapid development of renewable energy sources is promoted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种面向多时间尺度电力电量平衡的储能优化配置方法及系统，获取系统历史运行数据，收集并整理全年的风电、光伏和负荷数据，得到净负荷数据；使用STL分解法对净负荷数据进行时间解耦，获得全年内净负荷的趋势分量、季节分量和残差分量；建立包含氢储能和电化学储能的多类型储能规划模型；分别建立包含各类约束的储能规划约束模型；对多类型储能规划模型进行求解，获得储能优化规划结果、各时间段的弃风弃光情况、各时间段内的切负荷情况及各储能的出力情况。本发明充分发挥氢储能和电化学储能的优势，将长时间储能与短时储能协调配合，以减少不同时间尺度耦合，推动可再生能源的持续快速发展。"
                }
            ]
